To install fssort, follow these steps:

1) Install the following prerequisites

   For compilation:
       cmake from
       http://www.cmake.org/

       pkgconfig from
       http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/pkg-config/

   For compilation and runtime:
       e2fsprogs libraries from
       http://e2fsprogs.sourceforge.net/

	   libcap library from
	   http://www.friedhoff.org/posixfilecaps.html

2) Change directory into the top of the fssort source tree

3) Configure the build system by calling
   cmake .

4) Compile the program
   make

5) Install the program
   make install
